item.title: List of what I worked on ...
item.description: I have worked on a few interesting project but have not had the time to put them here. You can check out my github and send me a message on LinkedIn if you are interested. So far, I have worked on: Mobile Development in React Native: Google map mobile app focused on Concordia University’s campus and indoor directions for students, faculty and staff. Basic of machine learning (in pure python): Implemented a Naive Bayes Classifier to distinguish tweets language.
